    "title": "Ardhi",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "ardhi",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Ardhi ilikuwa muhimu sana kwa Waisraeli wa kale kwa sababu kilimo kilikuwa njia kuu ya kujipatia riziki. Waisraeli wengi walikuwa wakulima au wachungaji, na maisha yao yalitegemea uwezo wa ardhi kuzalisha mazao na kusaidia mifugo.</p><p>Mungu aliwapa Waisraeli nafasi na jukumu la kuishi Kanaani. Hii ilikuwa sehemu ya agano la Mungu na Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:33-1Kgs8:40\">1 Wafalme 8:33–40</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:68\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 28</a>). Ardhi ilikuwa kiini cha uhusiano wa Israeli na Mungu, ambaye aliiahidi kwa Abrahamu na kizazi chake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">Mwanzo 12:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:14-Gen13:17\">13:14–17</a>). Taifa la Israeli liliishi kama wale waliotunza na kumiliki ardhi. Ardhi ilikuwa &quot;urithi&quot; wa Israeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:21\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 4:21</a>). Mungu aliwapa na alihitaji uaminifu wao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:40\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 4:40</a>). Mungu alitarajia watu wasimamie ardhi vizuri na kumtumikia kwa uaminifu.</p><p>Kwa huzuni, watu wa Mungu walichagua njia zao wenyewe za kuishi. Walimwabudu miungu ya kipagani na kujitolea wao wenyewe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:7-2Kgs17:17\">2 Wafalme 17:7–17</a>). Hivyo basi, Mungu aliruhusu mataifa ya kigeni kuchukua ardhi ya Israeli polepole (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:20-2Kgs8:22\">2 Wafalme 8:20–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:1-2Kgs13:3\">13:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:3\">17:3</a>). Hatimaye, Ashuru ilivamia ufalme wa kaskazini na kupeleka Waisraeli uhamishoni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:5-2Kgs17:6\">17:5–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:22-2Kgs17:23\">22–23</a>).</p><p>Kupitia matukio haya, Mungu alionya Yuda, ufalme wa kusini, kwamba wangeipoteza ardhi yao kama hawangetubu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:8\">2 Wafalme 21:8</a>). Kwa bahati mbaya, hawakutii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:9\">21:9</a>). Kutokuwa waaminifu kwao kulisababisha kufukuzwa kutoka katika ardhi na Wababeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:1-2Kgs25:7\">25:1–21</a>).</p><p>Uasi wa Israeli na kushindwa kusimamia ardhi ambayo Mungu aliwapa ni onyo kwetu. Mungu ametukomboa kupitia Kristo Yesu ili tuweze kuishi maisha ya uaminifu na yenye tija (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:16\">Yohana 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:10\">Waefeso 2:4–10</a>). Ikiwa hatutakuwa waaminifu na wenye tija, tunaweza kupoteza jukumu letu katika kumtumikia Kristo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:1-John15:2\">Yohana 15:1–2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:6\">6</a>). Kwa kubaki tumeunganishwa naye, tunazaa &quot;matunda mengi&quot; na kukua katika imani yetu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5\">Yohana 15:5</a>).</p><p>Watu wa Mungu mara nyingi wana tabia ya dhambi (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">Warumi 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8\">1 Yohana 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:10\">10</a>). Hata hivyo, Mungu yuko tayari kila wakati kusamehe na kurejesha wale wanaotubu na kuwapa baraka za agano lake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1 Yohana 1:9</a>). Yesu, ambaye anasimamia agano jipya kati ya Mungu na watu wake, pia ni Msaidizi wao mbinguni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:27-Matt26:28\">Mathayo 26:27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1 Yohana 2:1</a>). Hatimaye, wale wanaobaki waaminifu kwa Mungu watapokea baraka za mbingu mpya na dunia mpya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1 Petro 1:3–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:7\">Ufunuo 21:1–7</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">Mwanzo 12:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:14-Gen13:17\">13:14–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1-Lev26:46\">Mambo ya Walawi 26:1–46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:68\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 28:1–68</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:29-1Kgs8:51\">1 Wafalme 8:29–51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:3-1Kgs9:9\">9:3–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:18-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:18–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1\">Zaburi 24:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:11\">89:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:4\">1 Petro 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:7\">Ufunuo 21:1–7</a></p>",
